[Adjustable] With their unique design, with one slightly smaller than the other, these shelf organizers can be stacked on top of one another, nested, used separately, or even in an L-shape. Adjust them how you want to perfectly fit your kitchen space

[Versatile] They can be used in more than just the kitchen! Use them in the dining room as a way to elevate your table centerpieces, on your bedroom desk to organize your items, or even in your bathroom to neatly store your bathroom essentials
[Easy to Assemble] With their simple structure and included instructions, these kitchen cabinet organizers are easy to set up and use

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Assembly Tips and Vertical Space Recovered
reviews.reviewText: ***** ASSEMBLY TIPSSome reviewers stated they had issues with the pre-drilled pilot holes, wobbly legs and the screws themselves. I had none of these issues with my order.Others mentioned there is not much clearance to place a screw driver between the top of the shelf and the bottom of the leg. This is true. There is no cheapie short screwdriver included such as may be the case with other products. You will have about 4-5/8 to 4-3/4 inches to work with. It is easier to use a stubby or offset screwdriver. A number 2 phillips screwdriver tip works best. See photos #3 and #5. Photo #3 is the shorter leg. Photo #5 is an optional offset screwdriver.To make the screws easier to install, before attaching the legs screw in the screws about three quarters of the way into the shelf and then remove the screws. When attaching the legs only screw in enough to make the legs secure.The pilot holes on my shelves did not line up exactly center to center, but the entire holes were visible. The legs attached without issue.***** OTHER DIMENSIONSIf you have a tight fit for some objects here are some dimensions not shown in the Amazon product page:The inside dimension between the legs on both shelves is about 10.0 inches (+/- 1/16 inch). See photo #4.The inside dimension from the bottom of the leg to the bottom of the taller shelf is about 5-5/8 inches (+/- 1/16 inch). See photo #6.The inside dimension from the bottom of the leg to the bottom of the shorter shelf is about 4-15/16 inches (+/- 1/16 inch). See photo #7.***** VERTICAL SPACE RECOVEREDI have a boat of spice containers in a kitchen cabinet resulting in wasted vertical space. These shelves solved a lot of my problem. I placed a turntable/Lazy Susan under each shelf. I settled on a Copco 9 inch diameter turntable. There were some other brands available in ten inch, but that may have rubbed on the shelf legs. See photo #8.***** OVERALL THOUGHTSThe shelves look good in just about any place you will use them. The quality is decent. The shelf dimensions are clearly given on the Amazon product page so there should be no surprises such as they are too small, too short, etc.***** MINOR ANNOYANCESEach shelf has paper labels attached to bottom of the shelf. Some paper and glue residue may be left on the shelf when the label is removed. See photo #9. There are labels that can be easily removed from wood, but this type was not used.I wont let packaging affect my overall review. It's worth mentioning. My order survived shipping thru delivery. Some reviewers complained about the shelf arrived broken. The shelves are packed in a box with no inside protection such as styrofoam. See photo #1. My box arrived in a gray shipping plastic bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very, very easy to assemble! Very sturdy. Beautiful appearance. Opens up space in small living areas.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Hard to Install but worth the money!
reviews.reviewText: Love this product for my cabinets!However, the screws are very hard to tighten into the wood with the Allen screwdriver it comes with. I highly reccomend using your own screwdriver and using small WASHERS (not included with the cabinet stands) (see photo) to elevate the hard to tighten screws. Without the washers, the stand may be very wobbly and difficult to tighten all the way down.The metal washers made installation so much easier and made the product even sturdier.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality!!! LOVE them!
reviews.reviewText: These are such great quality! I put them together with the hardware in less than 60 seconds. Very high-quality hardware as well. They are simple, yet give the look that I’m looking for and at a great price. We will definitely not be let down if you purchase these.!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great shelf set
reviews.reviewText: The shelf set looks great & seems very sturdy once assembled. But the provided Phillips head screwdriver tool is very hard to use. I had to get out my own tool. The manufacturer should have milled the short length of the L; this would offer easy of use. But, don’t over tighten the screws— the bamboo wood plank can crack & split…. a daub of wood glue fixed mine. Overall, the set is a good product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Listed as like new- not so much
reviews.reviewText: This is third order of these very nice shelves, but this was ordered as a like new product. Amazon quality control lacking as the shelves were definitely used, screws in bad shape and the “Allen wrench” needed to assemble was missing. Luckily I have pieces from other orders to use. Should have been sold at a lesser price than I paid. But these are great shelves to add storage that is lacking in our home!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what my cupboards needed!
reviews.reviewText: I have a lot of cupboard space, but it wasn’t being used efficiently because of all of the extra space between each shelf. I bought these with the hopes of doubling my cabinet space, and getting rid of some storage furniture that was holding my China and serving bowls. I am very happy with these shelves. They went together easily and are very sturdy and, they’ve done what I wanted them to and doubled my storage space in these two kitchen cupboards. I plan to buy more to more efficiently utilize all of my cupboard space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good and solid
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a small shelf to try to get some organization on my kitchen counter. Ran across this one and ordered it. It was difficult to get together. You have to put the screws in before you try to put it together so that the holes are already punched in. Then remove the screws and put the shelf together and it will be much easier. But once together I really liked it. Good and solid and with the wood type shelf things don't fall into the cracks. Worked really well.

Me costó un poco de trabajo armarlas y tuve que usar un destornillador que tenía en casa ya que el que estaba incluido se patinaba mucho. Fuera de eso, se ven muy bien y estoy feliz de aprovechar mejor el espacio de mi alacena, definitivamente compraré otro par más para seguir ordenando. Tengo varios productos Songmics en mi casa y soy fan, por lo general tienen gran relación calidad-precio.

reviews.reviewTitle: Muy bonito y de buena calidad
reviews.reviewText: Me gustó mucho, se ve muy bonito y tiene muy buena calidad

reviews.reviewTitle: Beautiful and great for small apartments!
reviews.reviewText: We needed a way to utilize the small space available in our apartment kitchen cabinets. These are a *fantastic* space saver. I was able to fit them into our pantry without any issue, and have been using them to store my cups on top of each other. This shelf divider is very easy to assemble (everything you need is included with the assembly), the measurements for it are accurate (since I was looking for something to fit snuggly), and it is sturdy.
Not quite like it is shown -- the edges are sharp and finish is not quite the same. But it is pretty sturdy and useful, nevertheless.
Este artículo es de buen material, vienen 2 por paquete de diferentes medidas y fácil de armar.Funcional para lo q los compré.
